{"tid":2349310,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到完場］ 2020年度叱吒樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮（6）","createTime":"2021-01-01T12:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T14:12:49.000Z","uid":349872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f49c71ad9d7d7eb546f58e7c66e62aaf301021","tid":2349310,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:44:29.000Z","msg":"2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮，是由香港商業電台舉辦的一個本地音樂頒獎典禮，將於<strong><ins>2021年1月1日晚上7時</ins></strong>於九龍灣國際展貿中心舉行，本屆頒獎禮雖恢復為實體形式，但將不設現場觀眾，以保持2019冠狀病毒病疫情期間的社交距離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8EF8fk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8EF8fk.png&h=fcdd18f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本屆主題定為「一切從音樂再開始」，美術主題為一輛叱咤火炬形狀的飛船在火星中準備起飛，帶領大家再次踏上奇妙的音樂之旅， 寓意誠邀大家一同登上飛船、重新向未知的將來出發。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>直播及轉播：</ins><br />\n叱咤903&mdash;聲音直播<br />\n<a href=\"http://my903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=bd8814c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://my903.com</a>、<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f2bc1418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://881903.com</a>&mdash;網上串流視像直播<br />\n手機程式 Hong Kong Toolbar（Android 用戶）、商台節目重溫 app / Hong Kong Toolbar（iOS用戶）&mdash;影片直播<br />\nViuTV&mdash;影片轉播"},{"pid":"c5e0d93c4ac794cbee4fa951dd07fe912ce45cad","tid":2349310,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4fc180035936826d6e8470c5337176bde778f988","tid":2349310,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"香港係屋企<br />\n多謝香港<br />\n講得好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfed119f3f9684e0f54d45533c77e30edd97d587","tid":2349310,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"